Write a program to check if the letter 'e' is present in the word 'Umbrella'.

Here's the program in Java that checks if the letter 'e' is present in the word 'Umbrella':

public class LetterCheckExample {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String word = "Umbrella";
        char target = 'e';
        boolean isPresent = false;

        // Iterate over each character in the word
        for (char c : word.toCharArray()) {
            // Check if the current character matches the target
            if (c == target) {
                isPresent = true;
                break;
            }
        }

        if (isPresent) {
            System.out.println("The letter '" + target + "' is present in the word.");
        } else {
            System.out.println("The letter '" + target + "' is not present in the word.");
        }
    }
}
